      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, what? what do you mean by \"goblin-proof\"? i'm just trying to fix the warehouse inventory. can we stick to the actual logistics causes? \n\nwhat are the most likely technical reasons for these specific numbers being off? like is it more likely to be a unit of measure error or just bad logging?",
